Package: rasterText
Type: Package
Title: Draw text to a raster
Version: 0.1.7
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Duncan", "Murdoch",
      email = "murdoch.duncan@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package is mainly intended as a 
  support for drawing text in the 'rgl' package, but should
  be usable by other packages that need to render text
  to a raster.  This can be done through R code or by
  direct calls to the underlying C code.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/dmurdoch/rasterText
BugReports: https://github.com/dmurdoch/rasterText/issues
SystemRequirements: pango, pangocairo, fontconfig
Config/build/compilation-database: true
